PrecisAppointment of GUY GIGUÈRE, of Ottawa, Ontario, as Deputy Chairperson of the Public Service Staff Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of two years; and orders that GUY GIGUÈRE shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act; effective April 1, 2001.
Attachments
precis:
Appointment of GUY GIGUÈRE, of Ottawa, Ontario, as Deputy Chairperson of
the Public Service Staff Relations Board, to hold office during good
behaviour for a period of two years; and orders that GUY GIGUÈRE shall be
deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public
Service Superannuation Act; effective April 1, 2001.
